Sentencas: Cobalt-free Sm0.6Sr0.4FeO3-delta-Ce0.8Sm0.2O2-delta (SSF-SDC) composite powders are prepared by a newly one-step synthesis method, co-synthesis method.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Powders XRD analysis shows that the composite powders exhibit the consistent phase structure with powders derived from traditional method, which demonstrate that the SSF is compatible with SDC.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Dry-mixing method, a traditional composite cathode preparation method, is used to obtain SSF-SDC composite cathode as a comparison.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The two cathodic composites of microstructures, electrical conductivities and symmetric electrochemical cells are characterized under the same condition.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: As a result, powders from new method show superior microstructure, high electrical conductivity and good electrochemical properties.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Finally, cathode preparing from new method is evaluated by an anode-supported SDC-electrolyte single cell testing.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: To further study SSF-SDC cathode, the thermal expansion coefficient and thermal cycling performance are measured.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The all results imply that co-synthesis method is a facile and practical way to improve the cathode properties and SSF-SDC is a promising cathode for intermediate temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: A cobalt-free composite cathode prepared by a superior method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
